{"tid":1784322,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［女神］出道快八年仍搭公車！AOA澯美外出沒人認得，私人生活更樸素到令人驚訝！","createTime":"2019-12-15T14:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T07:58:20.000Z","uid":71632,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2ccc3d954ccf232f4f66fbe217fb5e51c41f3f1a","tid":1784322,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T14:56:17.000Z","msg":"AOA澯美16歲就出道，是目前組合裡面年紀最小的忙內成員，不過年紀小小的她，生活可是簡樸到令人驚訝！<br />\n0留個言吧<br />\n近日澯美透過KBS節目公開了自己一天的生活，平時澯美沒有活動的時候，都是搭公車移動的，她透露自己開車太貴了，油錢、保險費、維修費用等等支出太多，所以都是選擇搭公車出入，讓節目主持人跟來賓們相當驚訝！<br />\nImage Source_Youtube| 슬기로운 어른이 생활<br />\n近日澯美透過KBS節目公開了自己一天的生活，平時澯美沒有活動的時候，都是搭公車移動的，她透露自己開車太貴了，油錢、保險費、維修費用等等支出太多，所以都是選擇搭公車出入，讓節目主持人跟來賓們相當驚訝！<br />\n0留個言吧<br />\n<br />\nImage Source_Instagram | chanmi_96a<br />\n主持人驚訝澯美身為大勢團體AOA組合的一員，難道不會被路人認出來嗎？澯美笑笑地表示：「自己從來沒有遇過這種問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">就連公車的乘客也沒有認出我過</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">澯美雖然才23歲，但也表示已經開始在擔心未來的養老費問題，平常最主要的花費只有在健身房上，吃飯也不會特別花大錢，就連美妝保養品都是選一定有打折過的購買。</span><br />\n0留個言吧<br />\n<br />\nImage Source_Instagram | chanmi_96a<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">節目中也拍到了澯美有各種會員積分卡，不放過任何一種可以累積會員點數的機會，仔仔細細算折扣價格的模樣，讓節目來賓都大讚澯美真的非常節省！</span><br />\n0留個言吧<br />\n<br />\nImage Source_Instagram | chanmi_96a<br />\n同時，澯美還表現出成熟的一面，表示正在和親姊姊一起給弟弟存大學學費。澯美說：「父母都給了我們這麼多，我們是不是應該給弟弟交一半學費呢？想讓弟弟去唸書的時候沒有負擔。」<br />\n0留個言吧<br />\n<br />\nImage Source_Instagram | chanmi_96a<br />\n澯美平時一個禮拜的生活費用，也低到令主持人相當驚訝，<span style=\"color: red;\">甚至有某天是「完全沒有任何支出」，她則解釋自己每天的行程除了運動就沒有別的了</span>，只要運動完後直接回家的日子，當天基本上就不會有支出。從節目中可以看的出來，澯美平時生活真的非常樸素呢！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好完美既女仔啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又大沒又靚心地性格又好又淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢咁樣生活應該仲未有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想娶佢做老婆啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46029a65f8b1f91a764fc6113f5dceae5768221a","tid":1784322,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1576419145.A.438.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FKoreaStar%2FM.1576419145.A.438.html&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=b5b6660a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1576419145.A.438.html</a><br />\n全部屌9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5fd344373e0166ebfee711ef8bb68b3df955cb8","tid":1784322,"uid":317979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"46029a65f8b1f91a764fc6113f5dceae5768221a","tid":1784322,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1576419145.A.438.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FKoreaStar%2FM.1576419145.A.438.html&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=b5b6660a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreaStar/M.1576419145.A.438.html</a><br />\n全部屌9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T15:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eeaa51a5d48a56a9053b54ae51a5b518290fd76","tid":1784322,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,